<title>SINGAPORE: Roly director raises stake in Roly.</title>
<headline>Roly director raises stake in Roly.</headline>
<dateline>SINGAPORE 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Roly International Holdings Ltd said on Tuesday its director Wang Lu-Yen had acquired 2.2 million Roly's shares averaging US$0.5471 each.</p>
<p>Wang's purchase raised his stake in the home decor and consumer product company to 29.76 percent from 29.08 percent, a company statement said.</p>
<p>-- Singapore Newsroom (65-8703080)</p>
